item.title: CVE-2024-8091|2024-09-17T06:00:06.131Z -- unknown -- enhanced%20search%20box
item.description: The Enhanced Search Box WordPress plugin through 0.6.1 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack
